id":836963,"uid":113064,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"百里香 故名思義<br />\n方圓百里都聞到嘅香味<br />\n你條<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>二五仔</strong></span>聞到香味都唔去食<br />\n枉你仲係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n依加過埋檔<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">以後唔洗返嚟喇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16f322a97d6ad0af53830fd0690a0ef0f9c2023","tid":836963,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"講下味道先<br />\n首先佢話係三杯 但係食唔出有三杯既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九層塔味都無 醬香味重 食落都幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n菜炒得好靚 食落口無渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送杯珍珠奶茶 呢杯野係有d失望<br />\n因為佢係整定一杯杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話忙起上黎沖唔切我明 但係奶茶可以整定 珍珠就等有人叫先落啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD珍珠完全無咬口 淋哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1b339fff00aa3f39b37ca52c23c3b71a3b1dd0","tid":836963,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78e181acd46444df72d21c90a94c627dc9a93443","tid":836963,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:41:00.000Z","msg":"依間上次百里香冇位食過，啲餸唔差但啲飯好撚淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw今日食咗薯仔沙律，應該係百里香有歷以來最正嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"同意 要求百里香將著仔沙律加入固定餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc87bcfec4ef8e85a4ef38639ff5adac06100921","tid":836963,"uid":4338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:41:58.